name: Dresselian Commando
Lore: 'Dresselians combat their homeworld''s subjugation with supplies provided by Bothans. The Alliance uses their talents as resistance fighters. These scouts prefer to work alone.',
Text: 'Power +1 when at a forest, jungle or exterior Endor site. When in battle at an exterior site against a non-unique alien, adds one destiny to power only, prevents opponent from drawing more than one battle destiny and is immune to attrition < 4.',
